Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:10.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やったポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:10.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,幹得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,さあ  今度はこっちの番だからね！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好了 現在該輪到我們出手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,おりろ！おりろっての！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,下來！給老子下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,おのれ...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可惡...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,立てザケンナー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們倒是起來啊胡鬧怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.48,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり  変身ポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.48,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光 變身吧！
