Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,將力量結合起來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:03.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,漲る勇気
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:03.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,昂揚之勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,溢れる希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,滿溢之希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光り輝く絆とともに！
